---
title: Creamy Pork & Roast Tomato Penne with Grated Parmesan Cheese
description: Packed with the rich flavours of a classic creamy tomato sauce, you'll find it hard to believe it didn't involve hours of cooking.
Silky baby spinach melts into the sauce, creating a mouth-watering meal everyone will love.
